        "playingGuide": "<h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';\">1.&nbsp;</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';\">How to register</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';\">• Fill in your phone number</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';\">• Set your own password (8 minutes with big and small letters and numbers)</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';\">• Confirm the password</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';\">• Click Remember password</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-famil