mes New Roman';\">Green: if the result shows 1, 3, 7, 9</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Red: if the result shows 2, 4, 6, 8</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Violet: if the result shows 0 or 5</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Small: if the result shows 0, 1, 2, 3, 4</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Big: if the result shows 5, 6, 7, 8, 9</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';\">• Play according to the rules of the game; you are not allowed to place illegal bets</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-far