lick the wallet icon</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';\"><br></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';\">•</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;<font face=\"Calibri\">C</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';\">lick the deposit button, and we have two methods to make a recharge (UPIPAY and USDT)</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';\">• Choose which method you want to use to make a recharge</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';\">• Select channel</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';\">• Insert the deposit amount</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p c