he amount you want to withdraw</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';\">•</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;<font face=\"Calibri\">Input your login password</font></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><img src=\"https://ossimg.51game-game.com/51game/editor/editor_202406091231004xbu.png\" style=\"width: 358px;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';\"><font face=\"Calibri\"><br></font></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';\"><font face=\"Calibri\"><br></font></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';\"><font face=\"Calibri\"><br></font></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';\"><font face=\"Calibri\">5. </font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Betting History</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';